name: State tribunal and support enforcement agency
text:
§576B-103  State tribunal and support enforcement agency.  (a)  The family court, the child support enforcement agency established by section 576D-2, and the office of child support hearings are the tribunals of this State.
     (b)  The child support enforcement agency is the support enforcement agency of this State. [L 1997, c 295, pt of §1; ren and am L 2015, c 77, pt of §1]
 
Note
 
  Section was former §576B-102.
